name: UnofficialMCUTrivia
0:
”Alexa, play Unofficial MCU Trivia”
”Alexa, open Unofficial MCU Trivia”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: unofficial m. c. u. trivia
des: Upon starting, Alexa will ask you a question, followed by a list of possible answers. Respond with your best guess of either one, two, three, or four. The goal is to get as many questions right as possible, with the highest possible score being five out of five.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
